rows.label: qev030605_MSG0001
rows.name: Bwa ha ha ha! Drink! Bring more drink![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030605_MSG0002
rows.name:
You! Take cup and join me. This is celebration!
Sobriety is disrespectful![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030605_MSG0003
rows.name:
Guh ha ha! Are you drinking? Here!
Toast to bride and groom![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030605_MSG0004
rows.name: Pace yourself, Uncle. You are not young.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030605_MSG0005
rows.name: Do not treat me like useless old man![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030605_MSG0006
rows.name:
I am still warrior! Rrgh! Someone bring me Cavern
clansman. I will flatten him in one blow![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030605_MSG0007
rows.name: Guh ha ha! Fresh air cleared my head of drink.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030605_MSG0008
rows.name: I am ready. Are you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030605_JNK0010
rows.name: Confirm

rows.label: qev030605_SEL0011
rows.name: Nod and drop into a combat stance.

rows.label: qev030605_JNK0020
rows.name: Beg Off

rows.label: qev030605_SEL0021
rows.name: Explain to Galba that you need a bit more time.

rows.label: qev030605_MSG0009
rows.name:
Then let us fight. May Nemard's marriage know glory
and good cheer.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030605_MSG0010
rows.name:
You face great hero. So go prepare.
I would hate you to suffer injury![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030605_MSG0011
rows.name:
Soft-bellied boy Nemard suddenly bears face of man.
It is good he does not lack resolve.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030605_MSG0012
rows.name:
Now he needs strength to defend his family from any
who threaten it. So I will beat boy into shape![ST:wait ]
